# Email Exists Request
This API checks to make sure the email is associated with Epic Games.
The API also needs to be captcha solved in order for the check to be ran.

*Updated 02/28/24*

## Request
| URL | Method |
|  -  |    -   |
| https://www.epicgames.com/id/api/email/exists | `POST` |

Example of payload:
```json
{
  "email": "DanielLogger124@outlook.com",
  "captcha": ""
}
```
